        "timestamp": "2019-04-15 08:19:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nCan you describe a little more on commit message what is failing and how this will fix it. I.e. failing to allocate some loop devices, but what that causes?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "24784d2ce355ff04eee0526d9f31a4a96db54cac",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5097,
