        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-15 08:37:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n> \n> Can you describe a little more on commit message what is failing and how this will fix it. I.e. failing to allocate some loop devices, but what that causes?\n\nDocker (in docker container) needs /dev/loop<X> to start at all and device nodes for loop device are not pre allocated on Centos whereas on Ubuntu they are, so no issues there.",
